data.description: Exceptional and spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on a 1.34 acre lot in beautiful Oak Springs Subdivision, St. Anne. Includes a 1 bedroom apartment above the detached garage equipped with heat, AC, Kitchen, full bathroom and a balcony! Perfect to rent out for some additional income or for related living! Enjoy Football Sunday's in the very expansive living room with electric fireplace. 4th bedroom works great as a home office with a full bathroom across the hallway. Master bedroom is massive and has plenty of closet space! Savor the breathtaking views in the Florida room with abundant natural lighting! Huge 2.5 attached garage and enormous detached garage and workshop area! Property being sold in "As Is" condition. This home is a must see!! Call today for your private showing!
